data.description: Welcome to 90 Beasley Estates, a delightful three-bedroom, two bath home nestled on a generous .58-acre lot in Benson for less than $300k! The property is conveniently located close to I-40 and I-95. The heart of the home is the spacious living area, where you can relax and entertain. Large backyard with 5ft fence along with Wi-Fi garage door opener added! The functional kitchen features ample counter space. Outside discover a fantastic pre-wired shed with heating and air perfect for your very own man cave or any other use you desire. Deck freshly painted and seller paid Cinch Home Warranty included with purchase! Motivated sellers with recent Price Improvement, will consider $2000 cost assistance with acceptable offer!
